remix 2.1
---------

BUG FIXES

* string "NA" were sometimes not printed with ascii() (pandoc print)

* declare R >= 2.13.0 dependency in DESCRIPTION file

remix 2.0
---------

NEW FEATURES

* Support label() from package Hmisc (option label = TRUE)

* Basic univariate tests (option test = TRUE)

* Can now handle univariate survival analysis (new class of data supported: Surv). 

BUG FIXES

* Internal changes to take into account changes in ascii 2.0

DEPRECATED & DEFUNCT

* Drop "|" syntax (Finally, it is useless)
